                    button.icon-cloud(type='submit', name='subscribe') Sign me up!
            .line
                p
                    | Need to contact the team for other reasons ?
                    | Just use this trusty and decentralized tool called email by sending a message to 
                    a(href="mailto:contact@cozycloud.cc") contact@cozycloud.cc
                    | .

        section#community-cozy.highlight
            .line
                h4
                    | Join our community
                p
                    | We need your help to make sure we can build the best Personal Server around.
                    | Connect with us to get tech support, to share your thoughts, integrate your contributions or show off your brand new app.
                .line
                    p.mod.w33.left
                        a(href="http://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=cozycloud")
                           img(src='/assets/images/irc-logo.png', alt='IRC Logo')
                           br
                           | <strong>#cozycloud</strong> on irc.freenode.net
                    p.mod.w33.left
                        a(href='https://forum.cozy.io')
                           img(src='/assets/images/forum.png', alt='Forum Icon')
                           br
                           | Forum
                    p.mod.w33.left
                        a(href='https://twitter.com/mycozycloud')
                           img(src='/assets/images/twitter.png', alt='Twitter Logo')
                           br
                           | Twitter
                           
        section#hack.line.target.simple
            .line
                h4
                    | Create apps for your Cozy server and share them with other users
            .line.mt6
                .mod.w33.left
                    p.txtcenter
                        img(src="/assets/images/big-plus.png", alt="Plus Icon")
                    p.pa2
                        | Fast application development.
                        br
                        | Cozy speeds up your web app development.
                        | It provides you with ready to-go templates, a simple web framework, an ODM and many more helpers.
                        | No specific IDE is required, you keep your favorite editor!
                .mod.w33.left
                    p.txtcenter
                        img(src="/assets/images/javascript_logo.png", alt="JS Logo")
                    p.pa2
                        | JavaScript based.
                        br
                        | You can build your web app with a single language for client and server: JavaScript.
                        | Soon, we will support applications composed only of HTML5 and Javascript, no server will be required.
                .mod.w33.left
                    p.txtcenter
                        img(src="/assets/images/server.png", alt="Server Icon")
                    p.pa2
                        | App sharing made easy.
                        br
                        | You will distribute your app easily to the entire community by sharing the Git URL of your repository.
                        | No need to worry about deployment anymore!
            .line
                .txtcenter.mt6
                    a.button.mt6(href="http://cozy.io/en/hack/getting-started/")
                        | Start learning how to write your Web app now!


        section#leave.highlight
            .line
                h4
                    | We're not trying to lock you in
                p
                    | What is annoying nowadays with online services is that they lock you in.
                    | This is not what we intend to do with Cozy.
                    | That's why you have the capability to delete your data and leave the platform anytime you want.
                    br
                    | See for yourself by clicking the button below:
                .txtcenter.mt3
                    a.button(href="/en/host/uninstall.html")
                        | Uninstall Cozy

